+# Word Garden
+
+> Word Garden is a small TUI game designed as a more cheerful alternative to Hangman. It is intended as a slightly more adventurous "Hello World" project for testing AI-assisted software development. The game includes input validation, state management, a simple loop, win/loss conditions, and a friendly terminal interface.
+
+Word Garden is a friendly terminal word-guessing game. Guess the hidden word before the garden runs out of water. It is like Hangman, but with plants instead of gallows.
+
+## How to Play
+
+Run the game from the repo root:
+
+```bash
+python3 -m word_garden
+```
+
+With options:
+
+```bash
+python3 -m word_garden --difficulty easy
+python3 -m word_garden --difficulty hard
+python3 -m word_garden --ascii
+python3 -m word_garden --difficulty normal --ascii
+```
+
+## Options
+
+| Option | Values | Default | Description |
+|---|---|---|---|
+| `--difficulty` | `easy`, `normal`, `hard` | `normal` | Controls word length and starting water |
+| `--ascii` | flag | off | Uses plain ASCII symbols instead of emoji |
+
+### Difficulty levels
+
+| Difficulty | Water | Word length |
+|---|---|---|
+| Easy | 8 | 4–6 letters |
+| Normal | 6 | 5–8 letters |
+| Hard | 4 | 7+ letters |
+
+## Rules
+
+1. A random word is chosen and displayed as blanks: `_ _ _ _ _ _`
+2. Guess one letter at a time.
+3. A correct guess reveals all matching positions. The garden grows.
+4. An incorrect guess costs one unit of water and causes a weed to appear.
+5. Win by revealing the whole word before the water runs out.
+6. Lose if water reaches zero before the word is fully revealed.
+
+Invalid input (empty, multiple characters, numbers, symbols) is rejected and does not consume water.
+
+## Sample Screen
+
+```
+🌱 Word Garden
+
+Plant:  🌿
+
+Word:      G _ R _ E _
+Guessed:   A E G R
+Water:  4/6 💧💧💧💧
+Weeds:  2 🌿🌿
+
+Good guess! The garden grows.
+
+Guess a letter:
+```
+
+### ASCII mode
+
+```
+Word Garden
+
+Plant:  *
+
+Word:      G _ R _ E _
+Guessed:   A E G R
+Water:  4/6 [****--]
+Weeds:  2 [--]
+
+Good guess! The garden grows.
+
+Guess a letter:
+```
+
+## Exit
+
+Press `Ctrl-D` (EOF) or `Ctrl-C` at any time to quit cleanly.
+
+## Project Structure
+
+```
+word_garden/
+  __init__.py     — public API re-exports
+  __main__.py     — python3 -m word_garden entry point
+  game.py         — game state and rules (pure logic, no I/O)
+  words.py        — word list and difficulty-aware selection
+  ui.py           — terminal rendering (pure rendering, no I/O)
+  main.py         — game loop and argument parsing (only I/O module)
+tests/
+  test_game.py    — engine tests
+  test_ui.py      — UI and integration tests
+```
+
+## Running Tests
+
+```bash
+python3 -m unittest discover -s tests
+```
